subtitleNullable: Dog images labeled by dog breed
descriptionNullable:
### Content

This dataset contains dog images labled by dog breed. The dataset is collected from scrapping the website https://www.savour-life.com.au/  that lists dogs for adoption. The data collected includes all historical data up to mid-November 2021.

Please note this data might requrie cleaning, as small percentage of images are invalid. Also a small percentage are not even referenced in the csv file because they were missing the label for the dog breed.

The data contains a csv file and a folder of jpeg files. The csv has the following attributes:
- `DogId` : unique identifier for the dog. There might be a number of rows that has the same DogId
- `Breed`: Breed name / lable as advertiesed on the website
- `Image`: File name of the jpeg image in the attached folder
- `ImageNumber`: A number between 1 and 10. Sometimes the same dog has up to 10 different images, the Image number is used to indicate the order of the Image on the Ad. The row with ImageNumber=1 is the primary profile photo of the dog.


### Inspiration

The dataset can be used to build a classification model that can detect dog breeds.
